column1: Update: automatically populate channel tools and display visible saturation levels. This .csv contains links to all AAV-cjDAE8 mouse and marmoset histology datasets publically hosted on Neuroglancer (see descriptions of datasets at the bottom).

Each dataset is interactive, you can scroll through 2D image stacks of serial sections or 3D light-sheet images, toggle channels on/off, as well as adjust the brightness and saturation thresholds for each channel.
In the upper left corner of the neuroglancer browser, click on the label for each channel to toggle on/off in the multichannel composite.
To populate channel controls in the neuroglancer browser: in the upper right corner of neuroglancer window, click on the wrench icon (first icon left-hand side) and then select  "All controls".

Descriptions of Neuroglancer Datasets ("Dataset Key"):
AAV-cjDAE8-dTom Marmoset Systemic Injection: confocal image stack of midbrain ROIs with DAPI, aTH, dTom, and aRFP (cjDove-confocal_neuroglancer_precomputed)
AAV-cjDAE8-dTom and retroAAV-cjDAE8-EGFP Marmoset Local Injection: confocal image stack of midbrain ROIs with DAPI, aTH, aGFP, and aRFP (cjSwan-confocal-amplified_neuroglancer_dataset_per_section)
AAV-cjDAE8-dTom and retroAAV-cjDAE8-EGFP Marmoset Local Injection: confocal image stack of midbrain ROIs with DAPI, aTH, EGFP, and dTom (cjSwan-confocal-endogenous_neuroglancer_dataset_per_section)
AAV-cjDAE8-dTom and retroAAV-cjDAE8-EGFP Marmoset Local Injection: whole-slide epi image stack of serial sections with DAPI, aTH, aGFP, and aRFP (cjSwan-Epi-Amplified_neuroglancer_precomputed)
AAV-cjDAE8-dTom and retroAAV-cjDAE8-EGFP Marmoset Local Injection: whole-slide epi image stack of serial sections with DAPI, aTH, EGFP, and dTom (cjSwan-Epi-Endogenous_neuroglancer_precomputed)
AAV-cjDAE8-dTom Mouse Systemic Injection (5E+10 vg dose): whole-slide epi image stack of a series for each mouse with DAPI, aTH, dTom, and aRFP (MouseSystemic_5E10_neuroglancer_precomputed)
AAV-cjDAE8-dTom Mouse Local Injection (5E+11 vg/ml, 300 nl dose): whole-slide epi image stack of a series for each mouse with DAPI, aTH, dTom, and aRFP (MouseLocal_5E11_neuroglancer_precomputed)
AAV-cjDAE8-dTom Mouse Systemic Injection (5E+11 vg dose): whole-slide epi image stack of a series for each mouse with DAPI, aTH, dTom, and aRFP (MouseSystemic_5E11_neuroglancer_precomputed)
AAV-cjDAE8-dTom Marmoset Systemic Injection: 3D light-sheet microscopy dataset of whole hemisphere with aTH and aRFP (cjDove whole hemisphere)
